    <h2 class="subtitle" id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Nocturnal animals exhibit remarkable adaptations for 
low-light vision that inspire technological advancements in remote 
sensing. Understanding their biological systems enhances our ability to 
explore and understand environments where human vision is limited.</p>
